summary: I have a broad interest in (clinical) research, with a focus on nutrition, healthy lifestyle and cardiology. I love to work in the practical aspects of clinical research, with and for researchers and get especially energized during study start-up. With great project management skills, a helicopter view and good interpersonal skills, I am an asset to every research project.
